ParallelChunk.en:
This is certainly no triumph for Parliament; 

            on the contrary

        , it is a defeat - one that we shall regret for a long time to come.

We have not stood in each other's way, we have not allowed ourselves to be used; 
          instead
        , most of us have surpassed ourselves and taken on responsibility for the European public.

Firstly, we have not treated workers like numbers; 
          rather
        , we have placed workers' and other people's rights above all other considerations.
